36:52.344 --> 36:53.577
Rachel: Let me
help you with these.

36:53.579 --> 36:55.078
Organize a little bit.

36:55.080 --> 36:57.647
Oh, myron, hi!
Are you here to thank us

36:57.649 --> 36:58.915
For throwing you the
greatest bar mitzvah

36:58.917 --> 37:00.016
In the entire world?

37:00.018 --> 37:01.251
Because a note would've
been sufficient.

37:01.253 --> 37:02.352
Um, these words

37:02.354 --> 37:03.687
Are like poison on my tongue.

37:03.689 --> 37:06.189
Myron muskovitz is
the newest student

37:06.191 --> 37:07.757
Here at mckinley high,

37:07.759 --> 37:10.060
And he would like to join
the glee club.

37:10.062 --> 37:11.595
You're not my mother!

37:11.597 --> 37:12.896
You don't have to speak for me!

37:12.898 --> 37:14.097
Now get me my inhaler!

37:16.702 --> 37:17.901
(gasps)

37:17.903 --> 37:19.102
Ow!

37:19.104 --> 37:20.704
Hey, come back here!

37:20.706 --> 37:22.038
Don't touch the piano!

37:22.040 --> 37:24.107
(piano playing erratically)

37:24.109 --> 37:25.942
Wait, sue, how-how is this
even possible?

37:25.944 --> 37:27.377
Myron's 13 years old.

37:27.379 --> 37:29.279
Well, that's a very valid point,
william,

37:29.281 --> 37:32.249
And it's one i made
rather convincingly, i thought,

37:32.251 --> 37:35.218
And, uh, superintendent harris
chose to ignore it.

37:35.220 --> 37:37.954
Instead, he strong-armed myron's
middle school principal

37:37.956 --> 37:39.389
Into submitting a petition

37:39.391 --> 37:41.758
To the school board
stating that myron

37:41.760 --> 37:43.460
Is so prodigiously talented

37:43.462 --> 37:45.962
That the junior
high environment

37:45.964 --> 37:48.231
Was no longer suited to him.

37:48.233 --> 37:50.267
Wait, so what you're saying
is that the glee club just got

37:50.269 --> 37:52.068
A brand-new, highly talented
singer and dancer

37:52.070 --> 37:54.137
Who happens to be a member
of the superintendent's family?

37:54.139 --> 37:56.306
Wow, sue, that has got to burn.

37:56.308 --> 37:59.943
It is my dunkirk, william.

37:59.945 --> 38:01.411
(groaning)

38:01.413 --> 38:03.313
But it is just the first battle

38:03.315 --> 38:05.815
Of the great war
to end all wars.

38:05.817 --> 38:07.717
Hmn.
And in the words

38:07.719 --> 38:09.252
Of a former
vice presidential candidate

38:09.254 --> 38:11.988
And my personal lamaze coach,

38:11.990 --> 38:13.556
"i do not retreat."

38:16.895 --> 38:18.895
"i reload."

38:18.897 --> 38:20.897
You gonna jump at me again, sue?

38:20.899 --> 38:23.333
I just might.

38:23.335 --> 38:25.068
And then again, i might not.

38:28.840 --> 38:30.573
