<i>I had a plan.</i>

38:30.575 --> 38:32.409
<i>Make this school the best</i>
<i>in the state,</i>

38:32.411 --> 38:33.910
<i>Cement my reputation</i>

38:33.912 --> 38:35.612
<i>As the greatest educator</i>
<i>since mao,</i>

38:35.614 --> 38:37.180
<i>And then ride off</i>
<i>into the sunset</i>

38:37.182 --> 38:38.581
<i>On the back of one of the five</i>

38:38.583 --> 38:40.583
<i>Remaining black rhinos</i>
<i>on the planet.</i>

38:40.585 --> 38:43.586
<i>Instead, well, i find myself</i>
<i>right back where i began,</i>

38:43.588 --> 38:45.689
<i>With a singular,</i>
<i>unwavering mission.</i>

38:45.691 --> 38:47.524
<i>I thought i had decapitated</i>

38:47.526 --> 38:50.593
<i>That glee club,</i>
<i>lanced it like a genital wart,</i>

38:50.595 --> 38:54.531
<i>But it has emerged once again</i>
<i>from its feculent roots.</i>

38:58.103 --> 39:00.470
<i>And so here we are.</i>

39:00.472 --> 39:03.540
<i>I will spend the last few weeks</i>
<i>of my professional life</i>

39:03.542 --> 39:06.810
<i>Fulfilling what i now know</i>
<i>is my destiny.</i>

39:06.812 --> 39:09.379
<i>This may kill me in the end.</i>
<i>I may not survive</i>

39:09.381 --> 39:12.048
<i>One last charge</i>
<i>unto the breach,</i>

39:12.050 --> 39:13.850
<i>Dear friends,</i>
<i>but i swear to you,</i>

39:13.852 --> 39:15.285
<i>Oh, pretend people</i>

39:15.287 --> 39:16.886
<i>That i'm speaking to in my head</i>

39:16.888 --> 39:18.221
<i>And are very impressed with me,</i>

39:18.223 --> 39:20.790
<i>I will be</i>
<i>the last man standing.</i>

39:20.792 --> 39:23.126
<i>As the great khan once said</i>

39:23.128 --> 39:25.395
<i>To captain james t. Kirk,</i>

39:25.397 --> 39:28.732
<i>"from hell's heart</i>
<i>i stab at thee, william."</i>

39:28.734 --> 39:32.469
<i>They can bury me in this</i>
<i>hurt locker if they want to,</i>

39:32.471 --> 39:34.838
<i>But you</i>
<i>and your entire glee club</i>

39:34.840 --> 39:38.541
<i>Are going to be buried in here</i>
<i>with me.</i>

39:38.543 --> 39:39.976
Junior high's small potatoes.

